HEADWORD: Discountable
<hw>Dis*count"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Capable of
being, or suitable to be, discounted; <as>as, certain forms are
necessary to render notes <ex>discountable</ex> at a
bank</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Discountenance</ent>⟦br⟧
